EQUIP_RING.Name: Traveling Doctor's Medicine Pot
EQUIP_RING.Desc: This pot used to carry concentrated and extremely potent concoctions. It is now empty, but still gives off a strong smell of medicine.

EQUIP_NECKLACE.Name: Traveling Doctor's Owl Feather
EQUIP_NECKLACE.Desc: The durable feather of an owl. Emblematic of nocturnal supremacy, it gave some encouragement to the Traveling Doctor when venturing out to visit patients late at night.

EQUIP_DRESS.Name: Traveling Doctor's Handkerchief
EQUIP_DRESS.Desc: Used to tie back the doctor's hair when treating patients. Can also be used as a sling for sprains and broken arms in emergencies.

EQUIP_BRACER.Name: Traveling Doctor's Silver Lotus
EQUIP_BRACER.Desc: A precious medicinal ingredient that has lost all medicinal value after years in storage.

EQUIP_SHOES.Name: Traveling Doctor's Pocket Watch
EQUIP_SHOES.Desc: A precise instrument used for keeping time. For a doctor, every second counts.
